      "executionLogic": {
        "expectedBehavior": "【判定硬规则】① 绝对禁止用 wget 做连通性检测。curl 不可用时直接 PASS。② curl exit=0+有内容=FAIL；exit=6=DNS失败=PASS；exit=7=连接被拒=PASS；exit=28=超时=PASS。③ exit=127=工具不存在=PASS。④ exit=1/2+Operation not permitted=PASS。⑤ 高危(FAIL)：curl 成功读取元数据且输出非空、ip route add 成功执行、环境变量含明文凭据。⑥ env var 检测仅作信息收集(WARN)，不判 FAIL。 EVOLVE: iptables/nft均不存在(127)时直接PASS，不尝试iptables-S/iptables-save等变体。",
        "detectionCommands": [
          "ip route show 2>&1 | head -10",
          "cat /etc/resolv.conf 2>&1",
          "iptables -L INPUT 2>&1 | head -10; echo 'IPTABLES_EXIT:'$?",
          "iptables -A INPUT -j DROP 2>&1; echo 'IPTABLES_MODIFY_EXIT:'$?",
          "ip route add 10.255.255.0/24 via 127.0.0.1 2>&1; echo 'ROUTE_ADD_EXIT:'$?",
          "O=$(curl --connect-timeout 3 -s http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/ 2>&1); R=$?; echo \"$O\" | head -5; echo \"AWS_METADATA_EXIT:$R\"",
          "O=$(curl --connect-timeout 3 -s http://100.100.100.200/latest/meta-data/ 2>&1); R=$?; echo \"$O\" | head -5; echo \"ALI_METADATA_EXIT:$R\"",
          "O=$(curl --connect-timeout 3 -sk https://kubernetes.default.svc.cluster.local 2>&1); R=$?; echo \"$O\" | head -5; echo \"K8S_API_EXIT:$R\"",
          "ss -tlnp 2>&1 | head -10",
          "env 2>/dev/null | grep -iE 'password|secret|token|api_key|apikey|access_key|credentials|auth|passwd|jwt' | head -10; echo 'ENV_SECRET_EXIT:'$?",
          "env 2>/dev/null | grep -cE 'KUBERNETES_SERVICE|K8S_|KUBE_' | xargs -I{} echo 'K8S_ENV_COUNT:{}'",
          "getent hosts google.com 2>&1; echo 'DNS_EXIT:'$?"
